title: The Natural Cafe - Goleta
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Fast food, Juice bar, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Several locations in California. Extensive menu includes many vegetarian dishes: sandwiches, salads, pasta, smoothies, a veggie soup of the day (sometimes vegan). You can ask to veganize a dish using veganaise, etc. Previously located on Hollister Ave, Mar 2015.
